Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and the end of case where activity 'Payment Handled occurs

Name: Average time between 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases where the next activity is 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in successful payment cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases that were initially 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases leading to re-submission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases with direct approval paths
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases followed by 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR', aiming to identify bottlenecks in the approval process.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
